Titolo: Plastic Memories

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Plastic Memories (プラスティック・メモリーズ, Purasutikku Memorīzu) is a Japanese anime television series produced by Doga Kobo and directed by Yoshiyuki Fujiwara. The story was conceived by Naotaka Hayashi, who also wrote the screenplay, with original character designs by Okiura. The series aired in Japan between April 5 and June 28, 2015.

